South Africa’s Reserve Bank’s Leading Economic Indicator Declines by 0.9%

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-05-24T07:04:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/south-africa-s-reserve-bank-s-leading-economic-indicator-declines-by-0-9-.html
The South African Reserve Bank’s
leading economic indicator fell 0.9 percent to 135 in March from
the previous month, the central bank said on its website today.  The indicator was revised to 136.2 from 136.1 in February,
the bank said on its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  